---
title: Rosemary Lamb Burgers with Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Just like a burger loves fries, lamb loves rosemary! This clever re-working of a comfort-food classic is simple to make and packed full of little 'a-ha' moments. From the juicy lamb burger with sweet chili crema, to the healthier roasted version of a sweet potato fry. Yum!
